Title: In the Pines
Writer: Craig Johnson (book), Hunt Baldwin (developer), John Coveny (developer), Hunt Baldwin, John Coveny
Actors: Robert Taylor, Katee Sackhoff, Lou Diamond Phillips, Bailey Chase
Plot: After a wilderness leadership trip takes a dark turn, Walt and the team must track down a killer and missing teenaged campers. Branch, meanwhile, continues his unsanctioned pursuit of his shooter.
